        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "BugHerd creates tasks from feedback automatically. You can assign them to team members, set priorities, add labels, and track progress. It replaces the need for a separate bug tracking spreadsheet.",
